de.learnlib.filter.cache

Interface LearningCacheOracle<A,I,D>

  • Type Parameters:
    A - the (maximally generic) automaton model for which the cache stores information. See LearningCache
    I - input symbol type
    D - output domain type
    All Superinterfaces:
    BatchProcessor<Query<I,D>>, LearningCache<A,I,D>, MembershipOracle<I,D>, QueryAnswerer<I,D>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    LearningCacheOracle.DFALearningCacheOracle<I>, LearningCacheOracle.MealyLearningCacheOracle<I,O>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DFACacheOracle, DFAHashCacheOracle, MealyCacheOracle, SymbolQueryCache

    public interface LearningCacheOracle<A,I,D>
extends LearningCache<A,I,D>, MembershipOracle<I,D>
    A learning cache that also serves as a membership oracle.

    Malte Isberner
